{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dc566e2c49","title":"周恩来关于国务院各副总理分工问题的请示报告","origin":"根据中共中央文献研究室《“文革”十年资料选编》","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"637376a52d","index":0,"year":1975,"month":2,"day":2,"articleId":"dc566e2c49"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2b10a0b9f4","type":"title","text":"周恩来关于国务院各副总理分工问题的请示报告","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"4cf58060de","type":"paragraph","text":"中央政治局审阅后转呈主席批示","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"a2b7adc6ee","type":"paragraph","text":"四届人大第一次会议闭幕后，政治局常委会上曾初步谈了国务院各副总理分工问题。后来，在政治局会上，洪文同志曾宣布国务院和中央军委常委的分工由各自议定后报中央、主席审批。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"a91f6ca4b1","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七五年二月一日，国务院召开总理、副总理十三人的常务会议，中央军委常务副主席叶剑英、科学院院长郭沫若两同志列席。会议审定国务院各副总理分工如下：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"30634baf5a","type":"paragraph","text":"一、邓小平：主管外事，在周恩来总理治病疗养期间，代总理主持会议和呈批主要文件；","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"6f5dbfa4e8","type":"paragraph","text":"张春桥：主管文化、教育；","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"595fd30568","type":"paragraph","text":"李先念：常务，主管财政、贸易；","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"9a6454ed51","type":"paragraph","text":"陈锡联：主管国防工业和体育；","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"28c1d69a44","type":"paragraph","text":"纪登奎：常务，主管劳动工资和干部调配；","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"97d6b4c34c","type":"paragraph","text":"华国锋：常务，主管政法和科学；","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"ea38ea573b","type":"paragraph","text":"阵永贵：主管农业；","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"b16a85cbc7","type":"paragraph","text":"吴桂贤：主管卫生和轻工业；","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"84f7a51336","type":"paragraph","text":"王  震：主管交通和供销；","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"11e9ff7705","type":"paragraph","text":"余秋里：主管计划和工业；","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"183205a279","type":"paragraph","text":"谷  牧：主管建设和工业；","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"85e1222b4a","type":"paragraph","text":"孙  健：主管工业生产。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"857501b531","type":"paragraph","text":"二、上述常务副总理（李、纪、华）三人负责处理国务院日常事务。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"aef3319cf6","type":"paragraph","text":"三、上述两项分工得主席、中央批准后，即召开国务院全体会议在会上宣布，不另行文。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"fae243b85c","type":"paragraph","text":"谨报，请予审批。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"9e811c7aa6","type":"paragraph","text":" 周  恩  来一九七五年二月二日","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"},{"id":"39d73b315d","type":"paragraph","text":"注：此件是中央办公厅秘书局提供的周恩来手稿，毛泽东圈阅过。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49"}],"page":{"id":"1db2378a3d","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"dc566e2c49","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}